init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You're even more surprised when you realize that you're the queen bee.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You're not sure what to do.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Should you tell it to buzz off?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "How did you know I was the queen?" you ask.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I don't know what to do," you tell the bee.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bee then tells you that you have been chosen to lead the bees in a war against the humans.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "You are the queen bee and you must lead us.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You run and run until you can't run anymore.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You can't breathe, you can't move, you can't scream.
